  "body": "Running into more of these errors.\r\n\r\n```\r\nerror TS2742: The inferred type of 'NavbarBrand' cannot be named without a reference to '../../../../../node_modules/@chakra-ui/react/dist/types/styled-system/factory.types'. This is likely not portable. A type annotation is necessary.\r\n```\r\n\r\nExported all factory.types, as they are all used by utilities or other types that are exported.\r\n\r\n*EDIT*\r\n\r\nAll factory types need to be exported to fix the error. There is a duplicate `JsxStyleProps`, i've exported the one from factory instead.",
